From: Jasper Aorangi <3222409+spmp@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sat, 24 Jan 2026 08:15:20 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 04/18] Add waypoints and jump style properties to connector
 model

- Add JumpStyle type: 'none' | 'arc' | 'gap' | 'sharp' | 'line'
- Add waypoints property to store user-defined routing points
- Add jumpStyle property (default 'none')
- Add jumpSize property (default 10px)

Phase 1 complete - model schema extended for draw.io-style features.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
